data.name: 0000 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Waiting to hear a piano outside a locked music room is completely pointless.

data.name: 0001 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: If by some miracle I did hear a piano, I can't report it to Haruhi anyway.

data.name: 0002 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: In other words—it's a complete waste of time.

data.name: 0003 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Haruhi instructed me to head for the music room, but I decided to make a detour instead.

data.name: 0004 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Haruhi should already be in the library by now, so it's probably fine for me to head back.

data.name: 0005 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I can just tell Haruhi I didn't hear anything of note, after all.

data.name: 0006 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Nagato said that the situation is gradually becoming more serious.

data.name: 0007 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: If we don't make a move fast, I'm worried it'll be more than just the seven wonders…

data.name: 0008 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …and we'll instead be dealing with an entire occult academy.

data.name: 0009 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Though I bet Haruhi would love that.

data.name: 0010 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: As long as there's a possibility of world collapse, we ought to do something about it.

data.name: 0011 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Good grief, what a pain.

data.name: 0012 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I really wish that the righteous hero tasked with saving the world was anyone besides me.

data.name: 0013 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Huh…? That club member isn't here.

data.name: 0014 (393.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Oh, you again?

data.name: 0015 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Sorry to bother you again.

data.name: 0016 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Um, where's the guy who was writing sheet music?

data.name: 0017 (393.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: He left just a while earlier…

data.name: 0018 (393.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: I think he's probably gone to the music room.

data.name: 0019 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: The music room? Did I miss him on the way…?

data.name: 0020 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: As someone who always relates to the grass- hopper from The Ant and the Grasshopper…

data.name: 0021 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Being told the path of laziness is correct after having already put in the effort…

data.name: 0022 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: ...only makes me even more tired. If I had just waited there, he would've come right to me.

data.name: 0023 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I should've had more faith in my instincts.

data.name: 0024 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Though since I'm already here, I want to at least get some value for my troubles.

data.name: 0025 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Could you please show me the sheet music he was writing?

data.name: 0026 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Nagato said that something was compelling him to write the sheet music.

data.name: 0027 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: If that something was a data lifeform, the sheet music might contain some sort of clue.

data.name: 0028 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I mean it's only natural to assume so, right?

data.name: 0029 (393.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: Umm, we don't really want to show anything to outsiders… Huh?

data.name: 0030 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The president looked over his shoulder at the desk and tilted his head to the side.

data.name: 0031 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What's wrong?

data.name: 0032 (393.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: The sheet music isn't there. Maybe he brought it with him?

data.name: 0033 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Really now…

data.name: 0034 (393.ja) CLUB_PRES (部長氏)
data.value: You're an unlucky man.

data.name: 0035 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Yeah, I know.

data.name: 0036 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Getting mixed up in this mess in the first place was the ultimate misfortune.

data.name: 0038 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: With no other options, I ended up heading back to the music room, but…

data.name: 0039 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It's far… too far.

data.name: 0040 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Ever since I started attending here, I've always wondered…

data.name: 0041 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Why is this school so needlessly huge?

data.name: 0042 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: In this era of declining birth rates, I can't believe we have nine classes in the first year.

data.name: 0043 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: And we were dangerously close to getting a tenth…

data.name: 0044 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The old building with clubs and the main one housing the music room are at opposite ends.

data.name: 0045 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: You really do have to go from end to end.

data.name: 0046 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I'm not sure if I should resent the designer, Haruhi, or that Computer Society member... Hm?

data.name: 0047 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Someone with his back turned was standing right in front of me.

data.name: 0048 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I'd seen that back before—it's the Computer Society member who claimed to hear the piano.

data.name: 0049 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He has an oddly unsteady gait…

data.name: 0050 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Is he carrying something?

data.name: 0051 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I was about to call out to him, but remember- ing Nagato's words, I decided just to watch.

data.name: 0052 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: When you call it the traces of something transcribed on his brain, I don't get it at all…

data.name: 0053 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …but he's acting suspiciously enough that I'll proceed with caution.

data.name: 0054 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I know they've been staying overnight, but he's walking as if he hasn't slept for days.

data.name: 0055 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He keeps drifting in different directions as he moves, looking around aimlessly.

data.name: 0056 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …What on earth is he doing?

data.name: 0057 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: At that moment, he crouched down in the middle of the hallway.

data.name: 0058 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …A music box?

data.name: 0059 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He stood up and continued walking. It seems like he was holding a music box.

data.name: 0060 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: What's he doing placing a music box here?

data.name: 0061 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It's possible he's been wandering around, looking for a place to put it.

data.name: 0062 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He was staggering still, but he walked right off without even a glance in another direction.

data.name: 0063 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Watching him leave, I got closer to where the music box was placed.

data.name: 0064 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It certainly looks like a normal music box…

data.name: 0065 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But for peace of mind, it'd surely be best to show this to Nagato.

data.name: 0066 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I picked it up and closed the lid.

data.name: 0067 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Just when I was deciding whether to go straight to Nagato or follow the club member…

data.name: 0068 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Don't close the lid—!

data.name: 0069 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh…?

data.name: 0070 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I thought he had gone already, but he was running straight towards me.

data.name: 0071 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Don't stop it… Listen… You should listen to it too…

data.name: 0072 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What's up with this guy?!

data.name: 0073 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Sheet music in hand, he waved it around as he grappled with me.

data.name: 0074 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He stretched his hand out trying to snatch back the music box from me.

data.name: 0075 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Listen… Listen to the music…

data.name: 0076 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: No, that's not right. He was trying to open the music box's lid.

data.name: 0077 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Just wait a second!

data.name: 0078 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: You should listen too…!

data.name: 0079 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He wants me to listen to it?

data.name: 0080 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: This guy—who is clearly not in his right mind—wants to open the lid of the music box.

data.name: 0081 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: In that case—I probably shouldn't let him open it at any cost.

data.name: 0082 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I twisted my body to try and get it out of his reach.

data.name: 0083 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But his hand hit the music box, knocking it to the floor.

data.name: 0084 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The impact from falling caused the lid to open, but it didn't start producing sound.

data.name: 0085 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hm? Is it broken?

data.name: 0086 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Ughh…

data.name: 0087 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: In that very moment, he flopped to the floor as if his strings had been cut.

data.name: 0088 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The pages of sheet music he was holding scattered around the corridor.

data.name: 0089 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …What's going on here?

data.name: 0090 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I gave a cautious look at the broken music box and the club member on the floor.

data.name: 0091 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Ugh… Uhhhh.

data.name: 0092 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Looks like he's come to his senses.

data.name: 0093 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Huh…? Where am I? How did I end up here?

data.name: 0094 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He tilted his head and searched his surroundings—is it okay to trust him?

data.name: 0095 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …Oi.

data.name: 0096 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Hm? You're from the SOS Brigade, right? You came to ask me about the music room?

data.name: 0097 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: I was in the clubroom, wasn't I? How did I end up lying here?

data.name: 0098 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Do you remember that music box?

data.name: 0099 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Music box? No, not at all.

data.name: 0100 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What about that sheet music?

data.name: 0101 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Sheet music? This paper scattered around? I don't know…

data.name: 0102 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Seems genuine. So he wasn't conscious during that memory transcription Nagato spoke of?

data.name: 0103 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: In other words—he was being controlled by a data lifeform or whatever, right?

data.name: 0104 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Uhh, hmm—I can't remember…

data.name: 0105 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: The other members told me you were going to the music room to get an audio sample.

data.name: 0106 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: R-really…?

data.name: 0107 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You were moving unconsciously, right? You should get some proper sleep.

data.name: 0108 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: You're right… I'm gonna go do that.

data.name: 0109 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: He gave an honest nod and walked off.

data.name: 0110 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I gathered up all the pages of sheet music that were scattered around the hallway.

data.name: 0111 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: A music box and sheet music, huh? I'd better show these to Nagato.

data.name: 0112 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: This makes it pretty clear that a data life- form or whatever was actually controlling him.

data.name: 0113 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I have no idea what to expect next.

data.name: 0114 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hey, you from the Computer Society.

data.name: 0115 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: What is it?

data.name: 0116 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You may not remember it, but you're the one who wrote that sheet music.

data.name: 0117 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Huh—I did?

data.name: 0118 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: You were writing it like a man possessed.

data.name: 0119 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: I don't remember… Can you show it to me?

data.name: 0120 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Hmm… It's unfinished, but it's probably not a bad tune.

data.name: 0121 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Creating a masterpiece unconsciously—I can't be disappointed about that.

data.name: 0122 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: That ranked up from "not bad" to "masterpiece" suspiciously fast.

data.name: 0123 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: I thought the SOS Brigade were our enemies, but you seem like a nice guy. Thanks a lot.

data.name: 0124 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Actually, we'll probably drop by again later to ask various things, so I hope you don't mind.

data.name: 0125 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: You've got it rough too, huh?

data.name: 0126 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Please don't say it so earnestly. Anyway, I'd better go tell Nagato and Koizumi about this.

data.name: 0127 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Whatever these data lifeforms or whatever are planning—I haven't the slightest clue…

data.name: 0128 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I don't get the purpose of the music box, but first I've got to deal with this guy.

data.name: 0129 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I decided to follow the club member in order to not lose sight of him.

data.name: 0130 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh…? Where's he gone?

data.name: 0131 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I could have sworn he had just rounded the corner, but he was nowhere to be seen.

data.name: 0132 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Where did he go?

data.name: 0133 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Aghhhhhh—!

data.name: 0134 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hm—?

data.name: 0135 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The club member suddenly charged at me.

data.name: 0136 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Aghhhh! #W20#SE412#Q00Ahhhh! #W20#SE412#Q00Wahhhh—!

data.name: 0137 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: With sheet music in hand, he frantically swung his arms around in broad, sweeping motions.

data.name: 0138 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It wasn't hard to dodge his somewhat awkward, puppet-like attacks.

data.name: 0139 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: Agh—?

data.name: 0140 (393.ja) CLUB_MEM_B (部員Ｂ)
data.value: …Guh—

data.name: 0141 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Hey now…

data.name: 0142 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He had collapsed and wasn't getting up. He wouldn't move even when I poked him with my toe.

data.name: 0143 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: What sort of attacker falls over and passes out by themselves?

data.name: 0144 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: The Computer Society is really lacking in strength, huh.

data.name: 0145 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I don't even know why he attacked me all of a sudden, but he was moving strangely.

data.name: 0146 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The pages of sheet music he'd been holding were scattered about.

data.name: 0147 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Rather than attacking on his own, it seemed more like the sheet music was moving him?

data.name: 0148 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: This sheet music…

data.name: 0149 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It's definitely suspicious. I'd better take these back and show them to Nagato.

data.name: 0150 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: That club member is still unconscious, but if I wake him up he might attack me again.

data.name: 0151 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I'm a little worried, but I don't think I have any choice but to leave him here like this.

data.name: 0152 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I decided to take the sheet music straight back to the others.

data.name: 0153 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It's too risky. I don't want to disturb him and needlessly end up going for Round 2.

data.name: 0154 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I can't shake the feeling that this sheet music was controlling him…

data.name: 0155 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: But I guess for now I'll talk to Nagato and Koizumi and confirm it with them.

data.name: 0156 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: He was sleeping. Rather than just being passed out, it sounded like he was fast asleep.

data.name: 0157 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It seems like I can just leave him as is.

data.name: 0158 (393.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: For now I'd better go report what happened.

data.name: 0159 (393.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I decided to head back to the others.

data.name: 0160 (393.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Take the music box

data.name: 0161 (393.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Follow the club member

data.name: 0162 (393.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Take the sheet music

data.name: 0163 (393.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Don't take anything

data.name: 0164 (393.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Take the sheet music

data.name: 0165 (393.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: Don't take anything
